# Dimension: Mnemonic — Words-in-Words (词中词)

## Internal Word Validity
- Every internal word must be a CONSECUTIVE letter sequence within the target word. No letter-skipping.
- Must appear in left-to-right order. No reordering.
- Must be common, high-frequency words recognizable to a junior-high student.
- Basic indivisible words must output `false`.

## Formula Accuracy
- Format: `[熟词A](中文) + [熟词B](中文) + ...`
- Internal words concatenated must correctly reconstruct the target word's spelling — complete coverage, no missing/extra letters.

## Chant–Formula Coherence
- Chant must logically connect the internal words to the target word's meaning.

## Script 6-Step Framework
6 distinct paragraphs required: (1) 标准纠音, (2) 熟词搜索, (3) 画面还原, (4) 逻辑合成, (5) 家族关联, (6) 思维升华. Missing or merged = fail.

## Scene Logic
- Visual story must be built from the actual internal words in the formula.
- Must bridge logically to the target word's meaning.

## Prop Ban
- No physical teaching props. Only "on screen" or mental imagination.

## Tone & Style
- Real-time live-stream style, colloquial, speak to "XX同学". Reject rigid/AI tone.

